{% comment %}
  The 2AM Reality - Problem Agitation Section
  Makes the pain visceral and relatable
{% endcomment %}

<style>
  .warmmy-problem {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: #fff;
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .warmmy-problem-container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }
  
  .warmmy-problem-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }
  
  .warmmy-problem-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 42px;
    color: #191004;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  
  .warmmy-problem-subtitle {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: #3d2522;
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .warmmy-story {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f8f8 0%, #fff 100%);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .warmmy-story::before {
    content: '"';
    position: absolute;
    top: -20px;
    left: 30px;
    font-size: 120px;
    color: rgba(245,178,185,0.2);
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
  }
  
  .warmmy-story-text {
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #191004;
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }
  
  .warmmy-story-text strong {
    color: #f5b2b9;
    font-style: normal;
  }
  
  .warmmy-story-author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 15px;
  }
  
  .warmmy-story-avatar {
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  
  .warmmy-story-author-info {
    flex: 1;
  }
  
  .warmmy-story-name {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #191004;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }
  
  .warmmy-story-role {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #717171;
  }
  
  .warmmy-problems-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 30px;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
  }
  
  .warmmy-problem-card {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 30px 20px;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 15px;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .warmmy-problem-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }
  
  .warmmy-problem-icon {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    margin: 0 auto 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: rgba(245,178,185,0.1);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  
  .warmmy-problem-icon svg {
    width: 30px;
    height: 30px;
    fill: #f5b2b9;
  }
  
  .warmmy-problem-card-title {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #191004;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  
  .warmmy-problem-card-text {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #3d2522;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  
  .warmmy-problem-cta {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px;
    background: #fff7e2;
    border-radius: 20px;
  }
  
  .warmmy-problem-cta-title {
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #191004;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }
  
  .warmmy-problem-cta-text {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #3d2522;
    margin-bottom: 25px;
  }
  
  .warmmy-problem-button {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #000;
    color: white;
    padding: 16px 35px;
    border-radius: 30px;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .warmmy-problem-button:hover {
    background: #f5b2b9;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .warmmy-problem {
      padding: 60px 0;
    }
    
    .warmmy-problem-title {
      font-size: 32px;
    }
    
    .warmmy-story {
      padding: 30px 20px;
    }
    
    .warmmy-story-text {
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    
    .warmmy-problems-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
    }
  }
</style>

<section class="warmmy-problem">
  <div class="warmmy-problem-container">
    <div class="warmmy-problem-header">
      <h2 class="warmmy-problem-title">Every Night, The Same Battle</h2>
      <p class="warmmy-problem-subtitle">
        You're not alone. 87% of new mums struggle with night feeds. 
        The exhaustion, the crying, the guilt... we get it.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="warmmy-story">
      <p class="warmmy-story-text">
        "It's 2:47am. My baby is screaming. I stumble to the kitchen, trying to warm milk while she gets more upset. 
        <strong>By the time it's ready, we're both in tears.</strong> I tried everything - bottle warmers that take 
        forever, microwaves that create hot spots, even the hot water method that never gets it right. 
        I just wanted to feed my baby without waking the entire house."
      </p>
      <div class="warmmy-story-author">
        <img src="{{ 'customer-sarah.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="Sarah" class="warmmy-story-avatar">
        <div class="warmmy-story-author-info">
          <div class="warmmy-story-name">Sarah Mitchell</div>
          <div class="warmmy-story-role">Mum of 2, Melbourne</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="warmmy-problems-grid">
      <div class="warmmy-problem-card">
        <div class="warmmy-problem-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="warmmy-problem-card-title">Traditional Warmers</h3>
        <p class="warmmy-problem-card-text">
          5-7 minutes of crying while you wait. Not portable. Needs constant cleaning.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="warmmy-problem-card">
        <div class="warmmy-problem-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="warmmy-problem-card-title">Microwave Method</h3>
        <p class="warmmy-problem-card-text">
          Dangerous hot spots. Destroys nutrients. Never the right temperature.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="warmmy-problem-card">
        <div class="warmmy-problem-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="warmmy-problem-card-title">Hot Water Bath</h3>
        <p class="warmmy-problem-card-text">
          Takes 10+ minutes. Messy. Impossible when you're out. Still crying baby.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="warmmy-problem-cta">
      <h3 class="warmmy-problem-cta-title">There's a Better Way</h3>
      <p class="warmmy-problem-cta-text">
        What if you could warm milk in 60 seconds, silently, anywhere, at the perfect temperature every time?
      </p>
      <a href="#solution" class="warmmy-problem-button">Show Me How</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

